= Strategy =

(% class="box infomessage" %)
(((
**FactHarbor aims to solve the "Binary Fact-Check" crisis through multi-perspective automation.**
We focus on transitioning from simple verdicts to an interactive **Evidence Landscape**. Our growth strategy involves scaling through deep-reasoning backends for existing monitoring leaders.

🔗 **Project Repository:** [[FactHarbor on GitHub>>https://github.com/robertschaub/FactHarbor]]
)))

